        protected java.lang.Object normalize(java.lang.Object value)
        Converts the given value if it is an IData or IData[] compatible object to an ElementList or ElementList[] respectively.
        Parameters:
        value - The value to be normalized.
        Returns:
        If the value is an IData or IData[] compatible object, a new ElementList or ElementList[] respectively is returned which wraps the given value, otherwise the value itself is returned unmodified.
